data.name: Business Term Deposit
data.description: A Westpac Business Term Deposit lets you invest your money with the certainty of a fixed interest rate and a choice of terms.

features.additionalInfo: Customers can open account either by Branch, Phone or Online.
Statements sent includes confirmation, maturity, renewal and repayment advices
Interest is paid: Monthly, yearly or at Maturity (where the term is 12 months or less) or at the end of any notice period.

eligibility.additionalValue: Those with an Australian residential address and who are currently in Australia.
Should have an eligible business registered in Australia
Should be authorised to act on behalf of an Australian business

eligibility.additionalInfo: Ensure every signatory on an account is identified according to Westpac's ID standard
